  <h1 class="title-case-study">The Building Blocks of Apps</h1>

  <div class="collage-text formatting">
    <div class="grid-2">
      <p>Every once in awhile a product emerges that shifts the way people understand the world. Whether it’s physical with the automobile or digital with graphical user interface and cloud computing. We think of these products as so revolutionary, so unique in concept and exquisite in execution that their humble beginnings are often overlooked.
</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <p>Folks that build products understand the shaky beginnings of successful companies. The late nights. The hurried napkin blueprints. Products begin as delicate ideas and evolve with effort and practice. Despite advances in technology the development process hasn’t changed much; it has only become faster.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

