  <div class="full-up formatting">
    <h2>Building Blocks</h2>
    <p>Atmosphere is centered around the idea that sharing is mutually beneficial. To encourage re-use we needed to showcase packages in the best light possible. We started with typographic layouts whose treatment contributed to the feeling of space, ease and brevity. The aesthetic simplicity served to humanize the content in contrast with the information density behind the scenes.</p>

    <h2>The Atmosphere Score</h2>
    <p>When building the foundation of a product it’s essential to be confident in the integrity of it's component pieces. Often this requires a combination of user research, social validation, and code review. It’s onerous for an individual to do this for every package. We created the Atmosphere Score to make this assessment easier by collecting, analyzing and synthesizing quantitative data to highlight packages that have the greatest chance of being ‘right’ for you.</p>
  </div>
</div>

